title: 1938 Coupe de France Final
text: The Coupe de France Final 1938 was a <a href="soccer">football</a> match held at <a href="Parc%20des%20Princes">Parc des Princes</a>, <a href="Paris">Paris</a> on May 8, 1938, that saw <a href="Olympique%20de%20Marseille">Olympique de Marseille</a> defeat <a href="FC%20Metz">FC Metz</a> 2–1 thanks to goals by <a href="Vilmos%20Kohut">Vilmos Kohut</a> and <a href="Emmanuel%20Aznar">Emmanuel Aznar</a>.
